      </a>\n                                            </li>\n                                            <li class=\"-item c-arrow_link\">\n                                                <a href=\"/reform/solution/others\" class=\"-link\">\n                                                    <span class=\"-title\">その他をリフォーム</span>\n                                                </a>\n                                            </li>\n                                        </ul>\n                                    </li>\n                                    <li class=\"l-header__nav__item -sp-nav-open -reform-item -kitchen\">\n                                        <a href=\"/reform/solution/kitchen\" class=\"c-arrow_link -type-c\">\n                                            <span class=\"-title -kitchen\">キッチンをリフォーム</span>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </li>\n                                    <li class=\"l-header__nav__item -sp-nav-open -reform-item -bathroom\">\n                                        <a href=\"/reform/solution/bathroom\" class=\"c-arrow_link -type-c\">\n                                            <span class=\"-title -bathroom\">バスルームをリフォーム</span>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </li>\n                                    <li class=\"l-header__nav__item -sp-nav-open -reform-item -sanitary\">\n                                        <a href=\"/reform/solution/sanitary\" class=\"c-arrow_link -type-c\">\n                                            <span class=\"-title -sanitary\">サニタリーをリフォーム</span>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </li>\n                                    <li class=\"l-header__nav__item -sp-nav-open -reform-item -others\">\n                                        <a href=\"/reform/solution/others\" class=\"c-arrow_link -type-c\">\n                                            <span class=\"-title -other\">その他をリフォーム</span>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </li>\n                                </ul>\n                            </div>\n                            <ul class=\"l-header__column -other l-header__border-wrap\">\n                                    <li class=\"l-header__nav__item -large js-nav-item\">\n                                        <a href=\"/reform/case\" class=\"c-arrow_link -type-c -white \">\n                                            <span class=\"u-bp-vr_none\">事例紹介</span>\n                                            <span class=\"u-bp-vr\">事例</span>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </li>\n                                    <li class=\"l-header__nav__item -large js-nav-item\">\n                                        <a href=\"/reform/reassurance\" class=\"c-arrow_link -type-c -white\">3つのあんしん宣言</a>\n                                    </li>\n                                    <li class=\"l-header__nav__item -large js-nav-item\">\n                                        <a href=\"/reform/staff\" class=\"c-arrow_link -type-c -white\">\n                                            <span class=\"u-bp-vr_none\">スタッフ紹介</span>\n                                            <span class=\"u-bp-vr\">スタッフ</span>\n                                        </a>\n                                    </li>\n                                    <li class=\"l-header__nav__item -large js-nav-item\">\n                                        <a href=\"/reform/flow\" class=\"c-arrow_link -type-c -white \">リフォームの流れ</a>\n                                    </li>\n                                    <li class=\"l-header__nav__item u-bp-tab_none -large js-nav-item\">\n                                        <a href=\"/reform/subsidy\" class=\"c-arrow_link -type-c -white\">補助金について</a>\n                                    </li>\n                                    <li class=\"l-header__nav__item -large js-nav-item\">\n                                        <a href=\"/reform/news\" class=\"c-arrow_link -type-c -white \">お知らせ</a>\n                                    </li>\n                                \n                            </ul>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"l-header__contact_outer\">\n                                <ul class=\"l-header_contact\">\n                                <li class=\"l-header_contact__item\">\n                                    <a href=\"/reform/showroom\" class=\"-link -showroom\">ショールーム</a>\n                                </li>\n                                <li class=\"l-header_contact__item\">\n                                    <a href=\"/request/form/reform/\" class=\"-link -contact\">お問い合わせ</a>\n                                </li>\n                            </ul>\n                            <div class=\"l-header__nav__logo-area\">\n                                <a href=\"\" class=\"-link\">\n                                    <img src=\"/assets/img/common/logo.svg\" alt=\"長野都市ガス\" width=\"90px\" height=\"30px\">\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </nav>\n                <!--ボタン-->\n                <div class=\"l-header__button-area\" >\n                    <button class=\"l-header__button js-hamburger\"  type=\"button\" id=\"js-hamburger\">\n                        <div class=\"c-hamburger\">\n                            <span class=\"c-hamburger__line\"></span>\n                            <span class=\"c-hamburger__text\" id=\"js-hamburger__text\">MENU</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n    </header>\n<div class=\"l-main p-contact\">\n  <div class=\"c-article-header\">\n    <h2 class=\"c-article-title\">リフォームのお問い合わせ</h2>\n  </div>\n      <div class=\"l-container -medium -tab-small-medium\">\n    <div class=\"lead-area\">\n      <p>下記の注意事項をご確認のうえ、お問い合わせフォームにご登録下さい。</p>\n      <div class=\"p-contact__lead-wrap c-prev-link-wrap\">\n        <ul class=\"p-contact__list\">\n          <li>リフォームに関するお問い合わせは、リフォームご計画地が施工エリアの場合に限らせていただきます。<br>\n          <a href=\"/company/kyoukyu/\" class=\"-link\" target=\"_blank\">【施工エリア】長野都市ガスの供給エリア</a>\n          </li>\n          <li>お問い合わせ完了後、３営業日以内に、お問い合わせ内容について確認の上、ご連絡させていただきます。</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"p-contact__sub-wrap c-prev-link-wrap\">\n        <a href=\"/privacy/\" class=\"-link\" target=\"_blank\">お客さま個人情報の取扱いについて</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"p-contact__mailform-wrap u-bg-white\">\n    <div class=\"l-container -medium -tab-small-medium\">\n      <div class=\"l-spacer -medium -pc-medium\">\n        <form name=\"mainform\" id=\"mainform\" method=\"post\" action=\"\" enctype=\"multipart/form-data\">\n        <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"request_token\" value=\"376a8c3993063d44e58dba2824a01275\"/> \n        <div id=\"cont\">\n          <div id=\"contents\">\n            <article class=\"innerWrap\" id=\"form\">\n            <section id=\"formArea\">\n              <div class=\"formTable p-contact__form\">\n                <div>\n                  <dl class=\"p-contact__mailform__cont\">\n                    <dt class=\"-must -head\">お名前</dt>\n                    <dd class=\"-desc\">\n                      <div class=\"\"></div>\n                      <input type=\"text\"  name=\"name_kanji\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"お名前\" class=\"-input \" >\n                      <p class=\"-example\">例）長野　都市男</p>\n                    </dd>\n                  </dl>\n                  <dl class=\"p-contact__mailform__cont\">\n                    <dt class=\"-must -head\">ふりがな</dt>\n                    <dd class=\"-desc\">\n                      <div class=\"\"></div>\n                      <input type=\"text\"  name=\"name_kana\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"お名前（ふりがな）\" class=\"-input \" >\n                      <p class=\"-example\">例）ながの　としお</p>\n                    </dd>\n                  </dl>\n                  <dl class=\"p-contact__mailform__cont\">\n                    <dt class=\"-must -head\">ご住所</dt>\n                    <dd class=\"-desc\">\n                      <div class=\"\"></div>\n                      <dl class=\"p-contact__mailform__dl-list\">\n                        <dt>郵便番号</dt>\n                        <dd>\n                        <div class=\"-post-mark\">\n                          <div class=\"\"></div>\n                          <input type=\"text\" name=\"postal_code\" size=\"8\" maxlengdt=\"8\" value=\"\" style=\"ime-mode: disabled;\" placeholder=\"郵便番号\" onkeyup=\"AjaxZip3.zip2addr(this,'','pref','city','address');\" class=\"-input \" >\n                          <p class=\"-example\">例）388-9999</p>\n                        </div>\n                        </dd>\n                        <dt>都道府県</dt>\n                        <dd>長野県<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"pref\" value=\"長野県\"></dd>\n                        <dt>市町村</dt>\n                        <dd>\n                          <div class=\"\"></div>\n                          <select name=\"city\" >\n                            <option value=\"\">選択して下さい</option>\n                                                        <option label=\"長野市\" value=\"長野市\">長野市</option>\n                                                        <option label=\"中野市\" value=\"中野市\">中野市</option>\n                                                        <option label=\"須坂市\" value=\"須坂市\">須坂市</option>\n                                                        <option label=\"千曲市\" value=\"千曲市\">千曲市</option>\n                                                        <option label=\"上田市\" value=\"上田市\">上田市</option>\n                                                        <option label=\"東御市\" value=\"東御市\">東御市</option>\n                                                        <option label=\"小諸市\" value=\"小諸市\">小諸市</option>\n                                                        <option label=\"佐久市\" value=\"佐久市\">佐久市</option>\n                                                        <option label=\"山ノ内町\" value=\"山ノ内町\">山ノ内町</option>\n                                                        <option label=\"小布施町\" value=\"小布施町\">小布施町</option>\n                                                        <option label=\"御代田町\" value=\"御代田町\">御代田町</option>\n                                                      </select>\n                        </dd>\n                        <dt>町名番地等</dt>\n                        <dd>\n                          <div class=\"\"></div>\n                          <input type=\"text\" size=\"25\" name=\"address\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"町名番地等\" class=\"-input \" >\n                          <p class=\"-example\">例）鶴賀1017 マンション長野2号棟 101号室</p>\n                        </dd>\n                      </dl>\n                    </dd>\n                  </dl>\n                  <dl class=\"p-contact__mailform__cont\">\n                    <dt class=\"-must -head\">お電話番号</dt>\n                    <dd class=\"-desc\">\n                      <div class=\"\"></div>\n                      <input type=\"text\" size=\"25\" name=\"telno\" value=\"\" style=\"ime-mode: disabled;\" placeholder=\"お電話番号\" class=\"-input \" >\n                      <p class=\"-example\">連絡のとれる電話番号を入力してください<br>例）090-1234-XXXX　※ハイフン「-」込みでご入力ください。</p>\n                    </dd>\n                  </dl>\n                  <dl class=\"p-contact__mailform__cont\">\n                    <dt class=\"-must -head\">メールアドレス</dt>\n                    <dd class=\"-desc\">\n                      <div class=\"\"></div>\n                      <input type=\"text\" size=\"25\" name=\"email_COMPARE\" value=\"\" style=\"ime-mode: disabled;\" placeholder=\"メールアドレス\" class=\"-input \"  >\n                    </dd>\n                  </dl>\n                  <dl class=\"p-contact__mailform__cont\">\n                    <dt class=\"-must -head\">メールアドレス（確認）</dt>\n                    <dd class=\"-desc\">\n                      <div class=\"\"></div>\n                      <input type=\"text\" size=\"25\" name=\"email\" value=\"\" style=\"ime-mode: disabled;\" placeholder=\"メールアドレス（確認）\" class=\"-input \" >\n                    </dd>\n                  </dl>\n                  <dl class=\"p-contact__mailform__cont\">\n                    <dt class=\"-must -head\">ご希望連絡方法</dt>\n                    <dd class=\"-desc\">\n                      <div class=\"\"></div>\n                                            <label>\n                        <input type=\"radio\" name=\"contact_method\" value=\"お電話\" >お電話\n                      </label>\n                                            <label>\n                        <input type=\"radio\" name=\"contact_method\" value=\"メール\" >メール\n                      </label>\n                                          </dd>\n                  </dl>\n                  <dl class=\"p-contact__mailform__cont\">\n                    <dt class=\"-head\">連絡希望時間帯</dt>\n                    <dd class=\"-desc\">\n                      <div class=\"\"></div>\n                      <select name=\"desired_time\" >\n                        <option value=\"\">選択して下さい</option>\n                                                <option label=\"いつでも\" value=\"いつでも\" >いつでも</option>\n                                                <option label=\"平日9:00～12:00\" value=\"平日9:00～12:00\" >平日9:00～12:00</option>\n                                                <option label=\"平日12:00～15:00\" value=\"平日12:00～15:00\" >平日12:00～15:00</option>\n                                                <option label=\"平日15:00～18:00\" value=\"平日15:00～18:00\" >平日15:00～18:00</option>\n                                              </select>\n                    </dd>\n                  </dl>\n                  <dl class=\"p-contact__mailform__cont\">\n                    <dt class=\"-must -head\">お問い合わせ内容</dt>\n                    <dd class=\"-desc\">\n                      <div class=\"\"></div>\n                                            <div>\n                      <label>\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"selected_inquiry[0]\" value=\"0\" >リフォームの相談に乗ってほしい\n                      </label></div>                                            <div>\n                      <label>\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"selected_inquiry[1]\" value=\"1\" >見積が欲しい\n                      </label></div>                                            <div>\n                      <label>\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"selected_inquiry[2]\" value=\"2\" >資料が欲しい\n                      </label></div>                                            <div>\n                      <label>\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"selected_inquiry[3]\" value=\"3\" >ショールームを見学したい\n                      </label></div>                                            <div>\n                      <label>\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"selected_inquiry[4]\" value=\"4\" >その他\n                                                                  （「具体的なお問い合わせ内容」にご記入ください） </label></div>\n                    </dd>\n                  </dl>\n                  <dl class=\"p-contact__mailform__cont\">\n                    <dt class=\"-must -head\">部位</dt>\n                    <dd class=\"-desc\">\n                      <div class=\"\"></div>\n                      <div>\n                      <label>\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"selected_place[0]\" value=\"0\" >キッチン\n                      </label>\n                      <label>\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"selected_place[1]\" value=\"1\" >浴室\n                      </label>\n                      <label>\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"selected_place[2]\" value=\"2\" >トイレ\n                      </label>\n                      <label>\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"selected_place[3]\" value=\"3\" >洗面所\n                      </label>\n                      <label>\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"selected_place[4]\" value=\"4\" >居室\n                      </label>\n                      <label>\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"selected_place[5]\" value=\"5\" >外壁\n                      </label>\n                      <label>\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"selected_place[6]\" value=\"6\" >屋根\n                      </label>\n                      <label>\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"selected_place[7]\" value=\"7\" >外構\n                      </label>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                      <label>\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"selected_place[8]\" value=\"8\" >家全体\n                      </label>\n                      <label>\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"selected_place[9]\" value=\"9\" >その他（「具体的なお問い合わせ内容」にご記入ください）\n                      </label>\n                      </div>\n                    </dd>\n                  </dl>\n                  <dl class=\"p-contact__mailform__cont\">\n                    <dt class=\"-head\">具体的なお問い合わせ内容</dt>\n                    <dd class=\"-desc\">\n                      <textarea name=\"free_text\"></textarea>\n                      <p class=\"-example\">例）床暖房を導入したい。</p>\n                    </dd>\n                  </dl>\n\n                  <div class=\"p-contact__mailform__button-wrap\">\n                                        <p>入力内容をご確認の上、<br class=\"u-bp-tab_none\">「確認画面へ」ボタンを押してください。</p>\n                    <div class=\"p-contact__mailform__button\">\n                      <div class=\"c-blue-button\">\n                        <a href=\"\" onclick=\"submit_c('reform', 'confirm'); return false\" class=\"btn btBlue btnM -link\"><span>確認画面へ</span></a>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                                      </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </section>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        </form>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  </div>\n\n<footer>\n  <div class=\"l-footer__logo\">\n  <div class=\"l-footer__logo__inner\">\n    <a href=\"https://www.nagano-toshi-gas.co.jp/\"  target=\"_blank\" class=\"l-footer__logo-area \">\n    <img src=\"/assets/img/common/logo.svg\" alt=\"長野都市ガス\" widdt=\"120px\" height=\"40px\" >\n    </a>\n    <span class=\"l-footer__copy-right u-en\">&copy; Nagano toshi Gas. All Rights Reserved.</span>\n  </div>\n  </div>\n</footer>\n\n<script src=\"/request/form/web/js/app.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\tvar g_site_name = 'request/form';\n\tvar g_controllerName = 'reform';\n</script>\n\n<script src=\"//ajaxzip3.github.io/ajaxzip3.js\" charset=\"UTF-8\"></script>\n<script src=\"/request/form/web/js/picker.js\"></script> \n<script src=\"/request/form/web/js/picker.date.js\"></script> \n<script src=\"/request/form/web/js/legacy.js\"></script> \n<script src=\"/request/form/web/js/ja_JP.js\"></script> \n<script>\n$(function() {\n  // 郵便番号\n  $('input[name=\"postal_code\"]').on('blur', function(){\n    var val = this.value.replace(/-/g, '');\n    this.value = val.slice(0,3) + '-' + val.slice(3);\n  });\n});\n</script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n","finalUrl":"https://www.nagano-toshi-gas.co.jp/request/form/reform/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-23T23:10:09.239Z"}